This appendix provides complete proofs for all theorems, propositions, and lemmas presented in the main text. Each proof is self‑contained; where a result is imported from the literature, the appropriate citation is given and the proof is sketched with emphasis on its application to the Second Orbit framework. Novel contributions are marked accordingly.

